::Feline::

She gets up and follows them.  She catches up and puts her hand on 
Skulletron's shoulder. She whispered into his ear,"Don't worry 
handsome, This may be fun yet." She smiled at him. 

She walked up ahead and walked next to Zardus. She purred to him. She 
leaned near him and whispered, "You got a spark melting smile. You 
know that don't you?"
She walked next to him and smiled.
